history.content:
Hi everyone! IEEE Professional Development Committee opens up a Q&A platform for everyone to drop up to 2 questions. You can ask about interviews, research, internship, side projects, academic success, public speaking, or other topics we want. Our mentors will review the questions and answer them with our best care and knowledge. 

We want to try our best to help our community to get through this period and your questions will be really helpful for us to write the guidebook for the entire community.

The link of the form:

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeV69uwDunKjv3jtxw-EKZkfxs94aWDjpCYrBOEbPUcsMxCAQ/viewform?vc=0&c=0&w=1&usp=mail_form_link
